---

<section class="py-20 bg-white dark:bg-[#080808] text-slate-900 dark:text-white overflow-hidden relative border-t border-slate-200 dark:border-white/5">
  <div class="absolute right-0 top-0 w-1/3 h-full bg-gradient-to-l from-[#CC0000]/5 to-transparent pointer-events-none"></div>
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-6xl relative z-10">
    <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center gap-16">
      <div class="lg:w-1/2">
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black mb-6 uppercase tracking-tight">Profil <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-[#CC0000] to-[#ff4444] italic">PITCAR</span></h2>
        <p class="mb-6 text-slate-700 dark:text-white/70 text-lg leading-relaxed">
          Berdiri di tengah pandemi tahun 2021 dengan layanan home service adaptif, PITCAR Service kini telah bertransformasi menjadi bengkel mobil modern dengan standar <i>dealer</i> dan sistem manajemen berbasis ERP mutakhir.
        </p>
        <p class="mb-10 text-slate-700 dark:text-white/70 text-lg leading-relaxed">
          Saat ini kami menangani rata-rata 400-450 unit per bulan dengan dukungan lebih dari 350 pelanggan tetap di wilayah Purwokerto dan sekitarnya.
        </p>
        <div class="bg-slate-50 dark:bg-[#141414] border-l-4 border-[#CC0000] inline-block px-8 py-6 rounded-r-xl shadow-xl shadow-[#CC0000]/5">
          <h3 class="font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-sm mb-2 text-[#CC0000]">Visi Kami</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-900 dark:text-white text-xl font-light italic">"Hadirkan ekosistem perawatan mobil terbaik di Indonesia"</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="lg:w-1/2 grid grid-cols-2 gap-5 w-full">
        <div class="bg-slate-50 dark:bg-[#141414] border border-slate-200 dark:border-white/5 p-8 rounded-2xl hover:border-[#CC0000]/30 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-[#CC0000]/10 transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="text-[#CC0000] text-4xl mb-6">
            <i class="fas fa-car-crash"></i>
          </div>
          <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white text-lg uppercase tracking-wide mb-3">Service Berkala</h4>
          <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-white/50 text-sm leading-relaxed">Layanan inspeksi preventif dan perawatan terjadwal</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-slate-50 dark:bg-[#141414] border border-slate-200 dark:border-white/5 p-8 rounded-2xl hover:border-[#CC0000]/30 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-[#CC0000]/10 transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="text-[#CC0000] text-4xl mb-6">
            <i class="fas fa-snowflake"></i>
          </div>
          <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white text-lg uppercase tracking-wide mb-3">Sistem A/C</h4>
          <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-white/50 text-sm leading-relaxed">Spesialis diagnosa dan reparasi pendingin udara mobil</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-slate-50 dark:bg-[#141414] border border-slate-200 dark:border-white/5 p-8 rounded-2xl hover:border-[#CC0000]/30 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-[#CC0000]/10 transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="text-[#CC0000] text-4xl mb-6">
            <i class="fas fa-oil-can"></i>
          </div>
          <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white text-lg uppercase tracking-wide mb-3">Oli & Fluida</h4>
          <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-white/50 text-sm leading-relaxed">Penggantian oli transmisi otomatis dan mesin secara presisi</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-slate-50 dark:bg-[#141414] border border-slate-200 dark:border-white/5 p-8 rounded-2xl hover:border-[#CC0000]/30 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-[#CC0000]/10 transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="text-[#CC0000] text-4xl mb-6">
            <i class="fas fa-car-side"></i>
          </div>
          <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white text-lg uppercase tracking-wide mb-3">Understeel</h4>
          <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-white/50 text-sm leading-relaxed">Perawatan sistem kemudi, rem, dan suspensi kaki-kaki</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
